        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 2, 3: Pctaire1 phosphorylated NSF on serine 569 and reduced its oligomerization.\n\nFigure 4a: Pctaire1 (CDK16) was enriched in synaptic vesicle biochemical fractions prepared from rat brain.. Experimental description: Results, Figure 4 legend: \"Subcellular fractions of adult rat brain were obtained by differential centrifugation and extraction and subjected to Western blot analysis using various markers of SNARE and synaptic vesicle-associated proteins\"" ;
